inputs.text: A portrait of a majestic and commanding queen, chest-up. Her face is a masterpiece of grace and power, with high cheekbones, deep, intelligent eyes, and a regal expression that exudes both wisdom and authority. Her lips are slightly parted, as if she is about to deliver a decree that could shape the fate of nations. Her dark, intricately braided hair is adorned with delicate golden chains and pearls, cascading elegantly over her shoulders. A magnificent crown, encrusted with sapphires and emeralds, rests atop her head, its fine craftsmanship a testament to her royal lineage. She wears a flowing velvet gown of deep sapphire blue, embroidered with silver thread in swirling celestial patterns. Over her shoulders drapes a heavy fur-lined cloak, fastened at the front with an ornate brooch in the shape of a phoenix. Her slender fingers, adorned with rings set with rare gemstones, rest gracefully on the hilt of a ceremonial dagger, a symbol of both her wisdom and her ability to command. The background is softly blurred, revealing grand marble pillars and flickering candlelight, enhancing the atmosphere of regal splendor.
